63夸捞 1:1 The elder to the elect lady and her children, whom I love in the truth, and not only I but also all who know the truth,
63夸捞 1:2 because of the truth that abides in us and will be with us forever:
63夸捞 1:3 Grace, mercy, and peace will be with us from God the Father and from Jesus Christ, the Father's Son, in truth and love.
63夸捞 1:4 I was overjoyed to find some of your children walking in the truth, just as we have been commanded by the Father.
63夸捞 1:5 But now, dear lady, I ask you, not as though I were writing you a new commandment, but one we have had from the beginning, let us love one another.
63夸捞 1:6 And this is love, that we walk according to his commandments; this is the commandment just as you have heard it from the beginning--you must walk in it.
63夸捞 1:7 Many deceivers have gone out into the world, those who do not confess that Jesus Christ has come in the flesh; any such person is the deceiver and the antichrist!
