66拌 21:23 And the city has no need of sun or moon to shine on it, for the glory of God is its light, and its lamp is the Lamb.
66拌 21:24 The nations will walk by its light, and the kings of the earth will bring their glory into it.
66拌 21:25 Its gates will never be shut by day--and there will be no night there.
