66拌 22:6 And he said to me, "These words are trustworthy and true, for the Lord, the God of the spirits of the prophets, has sent his angel to show his servants what must soon take place."
66拌 22:7 "See, I am coming soon! Blessed is the one who keeps the words of the prophecy of this book."
