66拌 22:9 but he said to me, "You must not do that! I am a fellow servant with you and your comrades the prophets, and with those who keep the words of this book. Worship God!"
66拌 22:10 And he said to me, "Do not seal up the words of the prophecy of this book, for the time is near.
